    <title>pubdate <lnpid>id-IN05-38829</lnpid></title>
    <body>
        <ul>
            <li><sourcexml>pubdate[@ln.user-displayed]</sourcexml> becomes
                    <targetxml>doc:metadata/pubinfo:pubinfo/pubinfo:dates</targetxml>. The attribute
                is suppressed. However, the attribute value affects the conversion of pcdata for
                child <sourcexml>date</sourcexml>, as described below. <ul>
                    <li><sourcexml>date[@day @month @year]</sourcexml> becomes
                            <targetxml>pubinfo:pubdate[@day @month @year]/date-text</targetxml>. The
                        attributes are optional. Often, only <sourcexml>@year</sourcexml> is present.<ul>
                            <li>Conversion of pcdata depends on parent attribute value, as follows:<ul>
                                    <li>If <sourcexml>pubdate[@ln.user-displayed="true"]</sourcexml>
                                        then <sourcexml>date</sourcexml> pcdata is mapped to
                                            <targetxml>date-text</targetxml>.</li>
                                    <li>If
                                            <sourcexml>pubdate[@ln.user-displayed="false"]</sourcexml>
                                        then <sourcexml>date</sourcexml> pcdata is suppressed for
                                        target (and so do not generate
                                            <targetxml>date-text</targetxml>).</li>
                                </ul></li>
                        </ul></li>
                </ul></li>
        </ul>
        <example>
            <title>Source XML - <sourcexml>pubdate[@ln.user-displayed="true"]</sourcexml></title>
            <codeblock>

&lt;jrnl:body&gt;
    &lt;jrnl:info&gt;
        &lt;pubdate ln.user-displayed="true"&gt;
            &lt;date year="2002"&gt;April 3, 2002&lt;/date&gt;
        &lt;/pubdate&gt;
    &lt;/jrnl:info&gt;
&lt;/jrnl:body&gt;

           </codeblock>
            <title>Target XML</title>
            <codeblock>

&lt;doc:metadata&gt;
    &lt;pubinfo:pubinfo&gt;
        &lt;pubinfo:dates&gt;
            &lt;pubinfo:pubdate year="2002"&gt;
                &lt;date-text&gt;April 3, 2002&lt;/date-text&gt;
            &lt;/pubinfo:pubdate&gt;
        &lt;/pubinfo:dates&gt;
    &lt;/pubinfo:pubinfo&gt;
&lt;/doc:metadata&gt;

           </codeblock>
        </example>
        <example>
            <title>Source XML - <sourcexml>pubdate[@ln.user-displayed="false"]</sourcexml></title>
            <codeblock>

&lt;jrnl:body&gt;
    &lt;jrnl:info&gt;
        &lt;pubdate ln.user-displayed="false"&gt;
            &lt;date year="2010"&gt;2010&lt;/date&gt;
        &lt;/pubdate&gt;
    &lt;/jrnl:info&gt;
&lt;/jrnl:body&gt;

           </codeblock>
            <title>Target XML</title>
            <codeblock>

&lt;doc:metadata&gt;
